title: DWave
extract: D-Wave Systems, Inc. is a quantum computing company, based in Burnaby, British Columbia, Canada. D-Wave is the world's first company to sell computers which exploit quantum effects in their operation. ... The D-Wave One was built on early prototypes such as D-Wave's Orion Quantum Computer.
